        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To the world proclaim the kingdom’s gospel,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Nourish saints in homes with warm embrace,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All perfect in groups by mutual teaching,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And in meetings speak the words of grace."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The perfected saints, hence, the Body build;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Bride at last shall be prepared."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lo! The beachhead of the coming Kingdom;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The present age’s end declared!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How we yearn to see the King in glory!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In our lifetime may His coming be."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In the kingdom manifested fully,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Reign as kings with Christ—our hope we’ll see!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Make us ready, Lord—in Thy presence, meet—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "On spices’ mountain Thee to face."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then forever in the Holy City,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Loud and resoundingly we’ll praise!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
